      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride and she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It handles great on the road and I've kept up with it nicely. I'm super excited for it to find a new home where it'll be appreciated! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
