    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service to ensure mechanical longevity. The suspension maintains its original kinematics, offering the communicative steering and balanced chassis dynamics synonymous with the M-division. A mechanically sound specimen perfect for the purist driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
