    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle offers a fantastic blend of reliability and comfort for its next owner. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the driver-side door handle\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the interior remains remarkably clean and is a strictly smoke-free environment. The leather seating shows light creasing on the driver's bolster but remains firm and supportive, while the dashboard and trim are free of cracks or fading. All electronic features, including the heated seats, navigation system, and backup camera, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. It has been meticulously maintained with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent service included a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a fresh cabin air filter. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, ensuring you are ready for the seasons ahead.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
